org.shingo.shingoeventsapp.ui.recipients

Class RecipientDetailFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.shingo.shingoeventsapp.ui.recipients.RecipientDetailFragment

  • public class RecipientDetailFragment
extends java.lang.Object
    A fragment representing a single Recipient detail screen. This fragment is either contained in a RecipientListActivity in two-pane mode (on tablets) or a RecipientDetailActivity on handsets.
